*Počeli* smo da izlazimo na rančeve.(We started to go out to the ranches.)

*Počelo* je da svi mnogo rade.(Everyone started to work a lot.)

*Počeo* je da mrzi svoju porodicu.(He started to hate his family.)

*Počeli* smo da se družimo sa novim ljudima.(We started to socialize with new people.)

*Počela* je da peva u školskom horu.(She started to sing in the school choir.)